# Global Guardrails

- Never add rotating carousels, autoplay audio/video, particle backgrounds, or parallax effects.
- Never use neon palettes, purple-pink AI gradients, or decorative novelty fonts.
- Ensure all interactive elements are keyboard reachable with clear visible focus styles.
- Respect reduced-motion user preferences and avoid unnecessary animation.
- Label editorial types clearly (fact-check, opinion, investigation, partner content, update).
- Prioritize trust signals: source attribution, verification method visibility, and transparent timestamps.
